This implements the Trusted Computing Group's (TCG) TPM2 Software Stack (TSS).
This stack consists of the following layers from top to bottom:

    * Feature API (FAPI) as described in the TCG Feature API (FAPI)
      Specification along with TCG TSS 2.0 JSON Data Types and Policy Language
      Specification.

    * Enhanced System API (ESAPI) as described in the TCG TSS 2.0 Enhanced
      System API (ESAPI) Specification.

    * System API (SAPI) as described in the TCG TSS 2.0 System Level API (SAPI)
      Specification.

    * Marshaling/Unmarshaling (MU) as described in the TCG TSS 2.0
      Marshaling/Unmarshaling API Specification.

    * TPM Command Transmission Interface (TCTI) as described in the TCG TSS 2.0
      TPM Command Transmission Interface (TCTI) API Specification.
